The following is an overview of the year '''[[2015]] in [[Japanese literature]]'''. It includes winners of [[literary awards]], yearly [[best-seller]]s, title debuts and endings and deaths of notable Japanese literature-related people as well as any other relevant Japanese literature-related events. For an overview of the year in literature from other countries, see [[2015 in literature]]; for an overview of the year in [[manga]] (Japanese comics), see [[2015 in manga]].
