age link multi|Ryōe Tsukimura|ja|3=月村了衛}} for {{Interlanguage link multi|Dobaku no Hana|ja|3=土漠の花|lt=''Dobaku no Hana''}} *** {{Interlanguage link multi|Kazuma Hayami|ja|3=早見和真}} for {{nihongo|''Inosento Deizu''|イノセント・デイズ||Innocent Days}} ** Best Critical/Biographical Work: *** [[Masahiko Kikuni]] for {{nihongo|''Hondana Tantei Saigo no Aisatsu''|本棚探偵最後の挨拶}} *** Aoi Shimotsuki for {{Nihongo|''Agasa Kurisuti Kanzen Koryaku''|アガサ・クリスティー完全攻略||The Definitive Guide to Agatha Christie}} * [[Naoki Prize]]: ** {{Interlanguage link multi|Akira Higashiyama|ja|3=東山彰良}} for 流 ** {{Interlanguage link multi|Bunpei Aoyama|ja|3=青山文平}} for つまをめとらば * [[Nihon SF Taisho Award]]: ** ''Koronbia zero'' (Columbia Zero) by [[Kōshū Tani]] ** ''Toppen'' by [[Hiroyuki Morioka]] * [[Noma Award for the Translation of Japanese Literature]]: {{Interlanguage link multi|Kwon Young-joo|ja|3=クォン・ヨンジュ}} for [[Riku Onda]]'s {{Interlanguage link multi|Sangatsu wa Fukaki Kurenai no Fuchi wo|ja|3=三月は深き紅の淵を|lt=''Sangatsu wa Fukaki Kurenai no Fuchi wo''}} * [[Noma Literary Prize]] : {{Interlanguage link multi|Mayumi Nagano|ja|3=長野まゆみ}} for 冥途あり * [[Seiun Award]]: ** Best Japanese Novel: {{nihongo|''Orbital Cloud''|オービタル・クラウド}} by [[Taiyō Fujii]] ** Best Japanese Short Story: {{nihongo|"Umi no Yubi"|海の指星}} by [[Hirotaka Tobi]] * [[Sogen SF Short Story Prize]]: {{Interlanguage link multi|Iori MIyazawa|ja|3=宮澤伊織}} for 神々の歩法 * [[Tanizaki Prize]]: [[Kaori Ekuni]] for ヤモリ、カエル、シジミチョウ * [[Yamamoto Shūgorō Prize]]: [[Asako Yuzuki]] for ナイルパーチの女子会 * [[Yomiuri Prize]]: **Fiction: {{Interlanguage link multi|Hideo Furukawa|ja|3=古川日出男}} for 女たち三百人の裏切りの書 **Drama: [[Haruhiko Arai]] for この国の空
