The '''American Writers Museum''' is a museum of [[American Literature]] and writing that opened in [[Chicago]] in May 2017.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/ct-writers-museum-in-chicago-sets-opening-date-20170124-column.html|title=Writers museum in Chicago sets opening date|first=Steve|last=Johnson|date=|work=chicagotribune.com|accessdate=17 February 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/museums/ct-writers-museum-ent-1028-20151027-column.html|title=New American Writers Museum is slated to open in 2017 on Michigan Avenue|author=Johnson, Steve|date=27 October 2015|work=[[Chicago Tribune]]|accessdate=13 December 2015}}</ref><ref name=Parker/><ref name=Liebenson>{{cite news|last1=Liebenson|first1=Daonad|title=Fundraising begins for the American Writers Museum|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-06-21/features/ct-prj-0623-american-writers-museum-20130621_1_printers-row-journal-american-writers-museum-foundation-malcolm-o-hagan|accessdate=8 April 2015|publisher=Chicago Tribune|date=21 June 2013}}</ref><ref name=Russell>{{cite news|last1=Russell|first1=Anna|title=American Writers Museum: A Bookish Proposal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424127887323734304578543302502803598|accessdate=8 April 2015|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=13 June 2013}}</ref><ref name=David>{{cite news|last1=Wallis|first1=David|title=Start-up Success Isn't Enough to Found a Museum|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/03/20/arts/artsspecial/start-up-success-isnt-enough-to-found-a-museum.html|accessdate=8 April 2015|publisher=New York Times|date=19 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.beverlyreview.net/news/community_news/article_2339b4f8-ab53-11e6-b625-17d8c5dde88a.html|title=Beverly's Cranston named AWM president|author=|date=|work=beverlyreview.net|accessdate=11 December 2016}}</ref> The museum was designed by Amaze Design of Boston.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.architecturaldigest.com/story/museum-writers-chicagos-michigan-avenue|title=American Writers Museum Set to Open on Chicago's Michigan Avenue - |first=Andrew|last=Zaleski|date=|work=Architectural Digest|accessdate=11 December 2016}}</ref>
The new museum was inspired by the [[Dublin Writers Museum]].<ref name=Parker>{{cite news|last1=Parker|first1=Loanne|title=Which Museums Show Real Promise?|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/lifestyle/style/which-museums-show-real-promise/2014/03/28/2a8ecffa-b6bd-11e3-a7c6-70cf2db17781_graphic.html|accessdate=8 April 2015|publisher=Washington Post|date=28 March 2014}}</ref>
